  "Title": "An update for curl is now available for openEuler-20.03-LTS-SP4,openEuler-22.03-LTS-SP4,openEuler-24.03-LTS,openEuler-24.03-LTS-SP1,openEuler-24.03-LTS-SP2,openEuler-24.03-LTS-SP3",
